Aia i loko o ka ʻai Peruvian ka ʻuala ma ke ʻano he kumu mua i nā kīʻaha he nui, ʻoiai ma kahi o 3,000 mau ʻano o kēia ʻuala i ulu ʻia ma laila. [95] ʻO kekahi o nā kīʻaha kaulana loa, ʻo ia ka ʻuala i hoʻolapalapa ʻia i kumu no nā kīʻaha he nui a i ʻole me nā kīʻaha ají e like me ka Papa a la Huancaína a i ʻole ka ocopa, ka ʻuala i kālai ʻia no ka hoʻohana ʻana i nā sopa e like me ka cau cau, a i ʻole ma Carapulca me ka maloʻo . ʻuala (papa seca). Hoʻohana ʻia ka ʻuala i kālai ʻia i ka causa Limeña a me ka papa rellena . ʻO ka ʻuala paʻi Palani kahi mea maʻamau i loko o nā mea hoʻouluulu Peruvian, me ka lomo saltado kīʻaha maʻamau .

He hua ʻuala maloʻo maloʻo ʻo Chuño i hana maʻamau e nā kaiāulu Quechua a me Aymara o Peru a me Bolivia , [96] a ʻike ʻia ma nā ʻāina like ʻole o ʻAmelika Hema, me Peru , Bolivia, Argentina , a me Chile . Ma Chile's Chiloé Archipelago , ʻo ka ʻuala ka mea nui o nā kīʻaha he nui, me ka milcaos, chapaleles, curanto a me chochoca. Ma ʻEkuador , hōʻike ʻia ka ʻuala, a ʻo ia hoʻi kahi meaʻai me ka hapa nui o nā kīʻaha, ma ka locro de papas puʻuwai., he sopa mānoanoa o ka ʻuala, ka ʻulaki, a me ka paʻakai.